---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Maestrokiller - 사지방 가속기">
	<div class="blur-overlay"></div>
	<main>
		<div class="hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="logo-container">
					<img src="https://i.imgur.com/FnMt3U4.png" alt="Maestrokiller Logo" class="logo-image" />
				</div>
				<h1>
					<span class="text-gradient">Maestrokiller</span>
					<span class="subtitle">사지방 가속기</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="hero-description">
					PC 환경(특히 '사이버 지식 정보방')에서 웹 브라우징 차단/필터링을 우회하고 
					Chrome 확장 프로그램을 자동으로 설치하여 사용자 편의성을 높이는 PowerShell 스크립트입니다.
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions">
					<a href="./Maestrokiller.ps1" class="download-button" download>
						<i class="fas fa-download"></i>
						<span class="download-text">다운로드</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<section class="features">
			<h2 class="section-title">
				<i class="fas fa-sparkles"></i>
				<span>주요 기능</span>
			</h2>
			<div class="feature-grid">
				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<i class="fas fa-puzzle-piece"></i>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-content">
						<h3>유용한 확장 프로그램 설치</h3>
						<p>uBlock Origin, Fastforward, Surfshark VPN, Volume Master를 Chrome 정책 레지스트리를 통해 강제 설치합니다.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-content">
						<h3>보안 프로그램 무력화</h3>
						<p>마에스트로웹5 및 맘아이 프로세스를 무력화하여 제한 없는 인터넷 사용이 가능합니다.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-content">
						<h3>VPN 서비스 지원</h3>
						<p>Surfshark VPN과 Proton VPN을 자동으로 설치하여 안전한 인터넷 접속을 제공합니다.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-content">
						<h3>자동 실행 기능</h3>
						<p>CCUpdater 및 cc2.exe(사지방 해제기)를 자동으로 다운로드하고 실행합니다.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="content-grid">
			<section class="setup glass-card">
				<h2 class="section-title">
					<i class="fas fa-wrench"></i>
					<span>설치 및 실행 방법</span>
				</h2>
				<div class="steps">
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">
							<i class="fas fa-terminal"></i>
						</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>PowerShell ISE 실행</h3>
							<p>반드시 <strong>관리자 권한</strong>으로 실행하세요.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">
							<i class="fas fa-key"></i>
						</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>실행 정책 설정</h3>
							<div class="code-block">
								<code>Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted</code>
								<button class="copy-button" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.previousElementSibling.textContent)">
									<i class="fas fa-copy"></i>
								</button>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">
							<i class="fas fa-play"></i>
						</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>스크립트 실행</h3>
							<div class="code-block">
								<code>.\HappyCom.ps1</code>
								<button class="copy-button" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.previousElementSibling.textContent)">
									<i class="fas fa-copy"></i>
								</button>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">
							<i class="fas fa-check"></i>
						</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>확인</h3>
							<p>크롬 브라우저를 재시작하여 확장 프로그램 설치를 확인하세요.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="side-sections">
				<section class="requirements glass-card">
					<h2 class="section-title">
						<i class="fas fa-laptop"></i>
						<span>시스템 요구사항</span>
					</h2>
					<div class="requirements-list">
						<div class="requirement-item">
							<i class="fab fa-windows"></i>
							<div>
								<h3>운영체제</h3>
								<p>Windows 10/11</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="requirement-item">
							<i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
							<div>
								<h3>필수 구성요소</h3>
								<p>PowerShell 사용 가능</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="requirement-item">
							<i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
							<div>
								<h3>권한</h3>
								<p>관리자 권한(Administrator) 필요</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="warning glass-card">
					<h2 class="section-title">
						<i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
						<span>주의사항</span>
					</h2>
					<div class="warning-content">
						<div class="warning-item">
							<i class="fas fa-shield-virus"></i>
							<div>
								<h3>보안 소프트웨어</h3>
								<p>알약, V3 등 일부 백신/보안 프로그램에서 경고나 차단이 발생할 수 있습니다.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="warning-item">
							<i class="fas fa-file-shield"></i>
							<div>
								<h3>정책/프로세스 종료</h3>
								<p>군 보안 환경을 우회하는 것은 제한된 영역에서만 사용해야 합니다.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	:root {
		--card-bg: rgba(23, 25, 35, 0.8);
		--card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		--hover-transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
		--icon-gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(var(--accent)), rgb(var(--accent-light)));
		--card-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		--accent-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(var(--accent), 0.2);
		--text-primary: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		--text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		--section-spacing: 4rem;
		--card-spacing: 2rem;
		--content-spacing: 1.5rem;
		--blur-strength: 10px;
		--blur-bg: rgba(19, 21, 26, 0.7);
	}

	.blur-overlay {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: var(--blur-bg);
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur-strength));
		z-index: -1;
	}

	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
		color: white;
		font-size: 16px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.hero {
		min-height: 70vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem 1rem;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-bottom: var(--section-spacing);
	}

	.hero::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		width: 150%;
		height: 150%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(var(--accent), 0.1) 0%, rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0) 70%);
		z-index: -1;
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur-strength));
	}

	.logo-container {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.logo-image {
		width: 150px;
		height: auto;
		animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
	}

	.hero-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		padding: 0 var(--content-spacing);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}

	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--icon-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 2em rgba(var(--accent), 0.2));
	}

	.hero-description {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.download-button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		background: var(--icon-gradient);
		color: white;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 100px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: var(--hover-transition);
		box-shadow: var(--accent-shadow);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.download-button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(var(--accent), 0.3);
	}

	.features {
		margin-bottom: var(--section-spacing);
		padding: 0 var(--content-spacing);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 var(--card-spacing) 0;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(var(--accent-light)), white);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.section-title i {
		font-size: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.glass-card {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur-strength));
		border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: var(--card-spacing);
		transition: var(--hover-transition);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.glass-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
	}

	.feature-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur-strength));
		border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		transition: var(--hover-transition);
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: var(--accent-shadow);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--icon-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		transition: var(--hover-transition);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding-top: 0.2rem;
	}

	.feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}

	.feature-content h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.feature-content p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.content-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
		gap: var(--content-spacing);
		padding: 0 var(--content-spacing);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.side-sections {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--content-spacing);
	}

	.steps {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--content-spacing);
	}

	.step {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.75rem 0;
	}

	.step-number {
		background: var(--icon-gradient);
		color: white;
		width: 3rem;
		height: 3rem;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		box-shadow: var(--accent-shadow);
		transition: var(--hover-transition);
	}

	.step:hover .step-number {
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}

	.step-content {
		flex: 1;
	}

	.step-content h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.step-content p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.code-block {
		position: relative;
		margin: 0.75rem 0;
	}

	code {
		font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		display: block;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.1);
		color: var(--text-primary);
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur-strength));
	}

	.copy-button {
		position: absolute;
		right: 0.5rem;
		top: 50%;
		transform: translateY(-50%);
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.15);
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2);
		color: var(--text-primary);
		width: 2rem;
		height: 2rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: var(--hover-transition);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur-strength));
	}

	.copy-button:hover {
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.25);
		transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.1);
	}

	.requirements-list, .warning-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--content-spacing);
	}

	.requirement-item, .warning-item {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--content-spacing);
		align-items: flex-start;
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.requirement-item i, .warning-item i {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.requirement-item h3, .warning-item h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.requirement-item p, .warning-item p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.warning {
		background: rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.2);
	}

	.warning .section-title {
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(255, 150, 150), white);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.content-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		:root {
			--section-spacing: 3rem;
			--card-spacing: 1.5rem;
			--content-spacing: 1.25rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		
		.subtitle {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.hero {
			min-height: 60vh;
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}

		.feature-card {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.feature-icon {
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding-top: 0;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.requirement-item, .warning-item {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.requirement-item i, .warning-item i {
			margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
		}

		:root {
			--section-spacing: 2.5rem;
			--card-spacing: 1.25rem;
			--content-spacing: 1rem;
			--blur-strength: 8px;
		}

		.logo-image {
			width: 120px;
		}
	}
</style>